value.0: This ancient looking stone is covered in lichen and marks from travelers long since past and dead. Still, engraved much deeper than anyone can defile is the name of the road the person is traveling upon...

Value.value: Further up the road, a large rocky spire rises towards the sky - clearly visible, even through the trees.
The bandits that plague the Lockwood Tradeway are harsh men and women, clearly just looking to earn a few coins.
